# SQL-PROJECT
# 🚀 Northwind SQL Portfolio

Welcome to my SQL project using the classic Northwind database! This repository includes a range of queries that demonstrate practical data analysis skills—from beginner basics to advanced techniques—structured to reflect real-world business scenarios.

## 📘 About the Project

The Northwind database simulates a company’s order and product data, making it perfect for practicing SQL in a business context. I've designed and solved multiple queries focused on insights like:
- 🛒 Top-selling products
- 🌍 Regional sales performance
- 👥 Customer segmentation
- 📈 Revenue trends

## 🧠 Skills Demonstrated

- SQL querying and optimization  
- JOIN operations and subqueries  
- Window functions and Common Table Expressions (CTEs)  
- Aggregation and filtering  
- Real-world problem framing and solution mapping  

